IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. UpdateAccountBalance.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-ACCOUNT-BALANCE    PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE ZEROS.
01 WS-DEPOSIT-AMOUNT      PIC 9(5)V99.
01 WS-UPDATED-BALANCE     PIC 9(7)V99.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    DISPLAY "Enter deposit amount: " WITH NO ADVANCING.
    ACCEPT WS-DEPOSIT-AMOUNT.
    
    ADD WS-DEPOSIT-AMOUNT TO WS-ACCOUNT-BALANCE GIVING WS-UPDATED-BALANCE.
    
    IF WS-UPDATED-BALANCE < 0
        DISPLAY "ERROR: Balance cannot be negative."
    ELSE
        DISPLAY "Updated Balance: " WS-UPDATED-BALANCE.
    END-IF.

    STOP RUN.
